ggplot2

ggplot(gapminder, aes(x = year, y = lifeExp)) + 
  geom_point()

Aussi possible avec des boxplots

ggplot(gapminder, aes(x = year, y = lifeExp, group = year)) + 
  geom_boxplot() + 
  geom_point()

line plot

ggplot(gapminder,
       aes(x = year,
           y = gdpPercap,
           group = country)) + 
  geom_line(colour = "darkgreen",
            size = 3,
            alpha = 0.1)

mapping to a group ‚Äì couleur par continent!

ggplot(gapminder,
       aes(x = year,
           y = gdpPercap,
           group = country,
           colour = continent)) + 
  geom_line()

facets

ggplot(gapminder,
       aes(x = year,
           y = gdpPercap,
           group = country,
           colour = continent)) + 
  geom_line() + 
  facet_wrap(~continent)
